x,y,z,w
x + y + z = w.
{(w−x)(w−y)(w−z) \over (w + x)(w + y)(w + z)} \le \frac 18
a = y+z, b = z+x, c = x+y
 \frac{ abc} {(a+b)(b+c)(c+a) } \leq \frac{1}{8}. 
AM-GM
 (a+b)(b+c)(c+a) \geq 2 \sqrt{ab} \times 2 \sqrt{bc} \times 2 \sqrt{ca} = 8abc
x=y=z
z>y>x
x^2 (y+z)+y^2 (x+z)+z^2 (x+y)\le2 \left(x^3+y^3+z^3\right)
